&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Fetch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fetchpet.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fetch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we’re dedicated to helping pets live their healthiest and happiest lives. Our comprehensive insurance coverage is designed with modern pet parents in mind, and we’re proud to support the veterinary, shelter, and breeder communities. We believe in ensuring pets receive the best care possible and are committed to making that vision a reality every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fetch is a high-growth&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://warburgpincus.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warburg Pincus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;portfolio company with an expanding team of over 350 pet-loving employees working together to shape the future of pet health and wellness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Industry&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The pet insurance industry is more important than ever, offering peace of mind and financial protection for pet owners. The sector is expanding quickly, fueled by growing awareness of the need for accessible, high-quality veterinary care. With advances in veterinary medicine, pets now have access to the most effective treatments available, making pet insurance an essential component of modern pet care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Actuarial Data Scientist&lt;/strong&gt; to help Fetch continue to have best-in-class pricing and profitability while also supporting growth of the business. You will leverage predictive analytics to improve the sophistication of our existing pricing models and build tools to monitor the performance of our rating plans over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this highly visible role, you will be a member of a small, close-knit actuarial team and will need to be adaptable, wearing multiple hats in support of various actuarial pricing and financial forecasting initiatives. Time will be roughly evenly split between pricing, conversion, and retention modeling work and traditional actuarial pricing work. You will help evaluate product proposals from a pricing and enterprise risk management perspective, support rate filings and responses to regulatory objections, and contribute to special pricing projects such as increased limit factor analyses, policyholder coverage utilization studies, and pricing brand new coverages. You will frequently engage in creative problem-solving and present your findings to senior leadership, actively shaping the organization’s future.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Remote (U.S.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Price Elasticity &amp;amp; Lifetime Value: &lt;/strong&gt;Develop price elasticity curves to forecast the impact of rating changes on policyholder retention and conversion, and assess their impact on customer lifetime value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conversion and Retention Forecast: &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Forecast policyholder retention and conversion for the portfolio based on pricing, operational changes, and business initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk Segmentation:&lt;/strong&gt; Improve the risk segmentation sophistication of our rating plans by developing GLM-based rating factors (in R or Python) and applying advanced predictive modeling techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Monitoring:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and maintain tools to monitor the performance of our existing rating plans and rate level over time, including loss ratio, conversion rate, churn, and lifetime value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Analysis &amp;amp; Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Write advanced SQL procedures to pull from large, line item level veterinary bill databases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;stron

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Fetch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fetchpet.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fetch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we’re dedicated to helping pets live their healthiest and happiest lives. Our comprehensive insurance coverage is designed with modern pet parents in mind, and we’re proud to support the veterinary, shelter, and breeder communities. We believe in ensuring pets receive the best care possible and are committed to making that vision a reality every day.&lt;/p&gt;
